{"tid":2172225,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"上水豪宅加按1億元, 持貨8年蝕1,100萬","createTime":"2020-08-24T12:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T16:50:28.000Z","uid":73269,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd1c5a9c339aac540bfc00a5110d19196e9826d","tid":2172225,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:39:29.000Z","msg":"上水洋房8年貶值1,100萬 曾加按1億元<br />\n上水知名豪宅St. Andrews Place亦有業主「出血」掟貨。消息指，CAMERON單號屋，實用面積3,344方呎，業主原本叫價5,500萬元，有指剛減至約4,800萬元易手，呎價14,354元。原業主2012年以5,900萬元買入，持貨8年賬面蝕1,100萬元，跌幅19%。查冊顯示，業主於2018年及2019年兩度將大屋作抵押，向財務公司借貸5,300萬及4,750萬元，總額超過1億元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200824/QI36U7ITDVDYJO5RETGSGPNHDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200824%2FQI36U7ITDVDYJO5RETGSGPNHDE%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbnIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=ca5d2d2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200824%2FQI36U7ITDVDYJO5RETGSGPNHDE%2F&h=dadae21d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200824/QI36U7ITDVDYJO5RETGSGPNHDE/</a>"},{"pid":"f034bac34710109825ff26eea6c184f4b1aaa82c","tid":2172225,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"mola mola"},{"pid":"88eaef7f9d21544713f609baeadf4d0ba671b2f2","tid":2172225,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"深灣原來係上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f7c49a895aeeaac4eb9127f447a14273c48361","tid":2172225,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88eaef7f9d21544713f609baeadf4d0ba671b2f2","tid":2172225,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"深灣原來係上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"scroll down"},{"pid":"70307f0943bc197fc68949112c28